<div class="container">

  <div class="d-flex flex-row justify-content-between">
    <div class="col-8">
      <h1><%= @kid.name %>, <%= @kid.localisation %></h1>
      <h2>Description</h2>
        <p>
          Un paragraphe est une section de texte en prose vouée au développement d'un point particulier souvent au moyen de plusieurs phrases, dans la continuité du précédent et du suivant.
          Sur le plan typographique, le paragraphe est compris entre deux alinéas, qui s'analysent aussi comme une « ponctuation blanche ».
          Le symbole du paragraphe est §. La fin d'un paragraphe était autrefois indiquée par un pied-de-mouche
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="col-4 d-inline-flex flex-column">
      <div>
        <% if @kid.photo.attached? %>
          <%= cl_image_tag @kid.photo.key, class: "avatar-xlarge" %>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <%= link_to "Book #{@kid.name}", new_kid_booking_path(@kid), class: "btn-flat" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex flex-row">

    <div class="col-4 ">
      <div>
        <h2>Masterized skils</h2>
          <div class="global-skill">
            <i class="fas fa-utensils" style="font-size:50px"></i>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>Cooking</h4>
              <p>Knows how to cook</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="global-skill">
            <i class="fas fa-drafting-compass" style="font-size:50px"></i>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>Drawing</h4>
              <p>Knows how to draw</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="global-skill">
            <i class="fas fa-tools" style="font-size:50px"></i>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>Building</h4>
              <p>Knows how to build</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2>Skills in progress</h2>
          <div class="global-skill">
            <i class="fas fa-paw" style="font-size:50px"></i>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>Pet-sitting</h4>
              <p>Knows how to cook a dog</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="global-skill" style="font-size:50px">
            <i class="fas fa-seedling"></i>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4>Gardening</h4>
              <p>Knows how to garden</p>
            </div>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-8">
      <div>
        <h2>Map</h2>
        <div id="map"
          style="width: 700px; height: 350px;"
          data-markers="<%= @markers.to_json %>"
          data-mapbox-api-key="<%= ENV['MAPBOX_API_KEY'] %>">
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="main-card-review">
          <h2>Reviews</h2>
          <div class="card-review" >
           <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/skateboard.jpg" />
            <div class="card-review-infos">
              <p>Maurice</p>
              <h2>Product name</h2>
              <p>Product description withrelevant info only.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-review" >
           <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/skateboard.jpg" />
            <div class="card-review-infos">
              <p>Maurice</p>
              <h2>Product name</h2>
              <p>Product description withrelevant info only.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-review" >
           <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/lewagon/fullstack-images/master/uikit/skateboard.jpg" />
            <div class="card-review-infos">
              <p>Maurice</p>
              <h2>Product name</h2>
              <p>Product description withrelevant info only.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

